data.description: Must See!!  This is a beautiful single-family home with many upgrades. This home has 5 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms. The main level has ½ bath, two living rooms, and a dining room. There is a brand-new custom kitchen with new appliances and a pantry, all appliances convey.  The main floor also has a laundry room and a bedroom with a full bathroom that can be used as a primary bedroom. The second floor has a primary bedroom with a newly updated bathroom. There are 3 other bedrooms located on the second floor. The roof is new, and the home has 38 brand new windows with easy clean title. There is also an unfinished basement with endless potential.
